title: WWE-TNA-ROH Dragon Gate USA 2014.04.04-05 x264
description:
Dragon Gate USA presents *
Open The Ultimate Gate 2014 
Friday, April 4th, 2014 

1. Open The Freedom Gate Championship Match: Johnny Gargano vs. 
   Open The Dream Gate Champion Ricochet 
2.Open The United Gate Championship Match: The Bravado Brothers w/ Moose defend vs. 
   The Premier Athlete Brand of Anthony Nese & Caleb Konley w/ Mr. A & Su Yung 
3. International Dream Match: EVOLVE Champion Chris Hero vs. Masato Tanaka 
4. Low Ki vs. Trent Baretta w/ Mr. A & Su Yung 
5. The Gentleman's Club of Chuck Taylor & Drew Gulak vs. The Colony of Fire Ant & Green Ant 
6. AR Fox vs. Mr. A w/ Su Yung 
7. Rich Swann vs. Biff Busick 

Dragon Gate USA presents *
Mercury Rising 2014 
Saturday, April 5th, 2014 

1. DGUSA Six Man Tournament First Round Match #1 
   Ricochet, Rich Swann & AR Fox vs. Chris Hero, Roderick Strong & Masato Tanaka 
2. DGUSA Six Man Tournament First Round Match #2 
   The Bravado Brothers & Moose vs. Fire Ant, Green Ant & Lince Dorado 
3. DGUSA Six Man Tournament First Round Match #3 
   Trent Baretta, Anthony Nese & Caleb Konley vs. The Gentleman's Club 
4. DGUSA Six Man Tournament Finals - Elimination Match 
5. Winner Of Match #1 vs. Winner Of Match #2 vs. Winner Of Match #3 
6. Special Main Event: Open The Freedom Gate Champion Johnny Gargano vs. Low Ki 

The Winner Of Ivelisse vs. Jazz At A Wrestling Odyssey Will Defend The SHINE Championship

*Source: XWT (The Audio sucks on these)
